content.title: Ukubukwa kokutholakala kokutholakala
content.howToUseTooltip:
Ngezansi kunezimpawu ezimaka zale ndawo ezingasetshenziswa ukukhetha imisebenzi, njengokuchofoza, ukugcwalisa umbhalo, njll.

Inani lemfanelo lingaphindwa ekhasini le-App. Uma uhlangabezana nezimpinda, sicela ubeke uploke ezinye izinketho zemfanelo ukuze unqume ubunye.

Igama elibomvu libonisa ukuthi inani lemfanelo liphindwa, igama eliluhlaza libonisa ukuthi inani lemfanelo lihlukile kusesho lwekhasi lamanje, futhi igama elimnyama libonisa ukuthi akukho ukuqhathanisa okuphindaphindwayo.
